Olori Aiyivieruewinoya "Ivie" Emiko-Atuwatse, nke a maara dị ka Olori Atuwatse III (amụrụ na 22 Mee 1986), bụ Ezẹ Nwanyị nke Alaeze Warri, onye ọka iwu, onye ọchụnta ego na nwunye Ogiame Atuwatse nke Atọ, onye na-achị alaeze Warri ugbu a, na Olu nke 21 nke Warri. Ọ bụkwa nwa nwanyị nke onye ọchụnta ego Naijiria, onye na-etinye ego na onye ọrụ ebere Captain Hosa Wells Okunbo
Mgbe e chiri ya ezẹ n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ 2021, Olu nke Warri nyere nwunye ya aha ọhụrụ, na-akpọ ya Olori Atuwatse III, ugbu a ọ bụ aha ya.
A mụrụ Olori Atuwatse na Lagos ma gụọ akwụkwọ na Naịịria na United Kingdom
O nwetara nzere Bachelor of Laws na London School of Economics ma kpọọ ya na Naịjịria Bar na 2010.

Olori Atuwatse III etinyela aka n'ọtụtụ mbọ na-elekwasị anya na ụmụ nwanyị na ụmụaka, gụnyere Captain Idahosa Wells Okunbo Stem Innovation Centre, nke o guzobere iji sọpụrụ nna ya. Ọ malitekwara ọtụtụ mmemme itinye aka maka ndị ogbenyé na Delta State, gụnyere nleta 2022 na Urejụ Community, ogige mmanụ jupụtara na ya na-ata ahụhụ mmetụta nke mmebi gburugburu ebe obibi na Iyara, obodo ogige ọzọ. Olori Atuwatse nke Atọ bụkwa onye na-akwado ikike ụmụaka, ọkachasị inye ụmụ nwanyị ikike

O nyela ọtụtụ narị ụmụaka agụmakwụkwọ, gụnyere atụmatụ 2022 maka ụmụaka 100 sitere na Nana Model Girls College Warri, Warri, Delta State. N'okpuru atụmatụ ahụike ya, Olori Atuwatse III akwalitewo ohere ịnweta nlekọta ahụike n'efu, ọkachasị maka ndị ogbenye, na Disemba 2021, malitere mgbasa ozi ahụike na ọdịmma Wuwu Ore, lekwasịrị anya na ụmụ nwanyị, ụmụaka na ndị agadi. E mere mbipụta nke abụọ nke mmemme ahụ na Ugbolokposo Community, na steeti Delta n'ọnwa Eprel 2022.
Olori Atuwatse nke Atọ lụrụ Ogiame Atuwatse Nke Atọ na Nọvemba 2014. Ha nwere ụmụ atọ.
